name: Glacier Maw Refrigerator
text: In the Frostbite Vale, the Glacier Maw Refrigerator stood, a titan among icicles. Where Inferno Maw devoured flames, Glacier's cool breath preserved. Once, a wayward traveler sought the fiery kin's warmth; instead, he found solace in Glacier's embrace, his provisions eternally fresh in her serene, icy heart.

data.revised_prompt: Imagine an icy landscape under the beautiful oscillating lights of the aurora borealis. In the center stands a large, personified refrigerator, its surface glistening with frost to signify its intense coldness, decorated with delicate snowflakes and hanging icicles. This refrigerator enjoys an aura of calmness, its gentle, satisfied face offers a striking contrast to a fiery image one might have of hunger. Through its partially open door, a soft blue glow and a light snowfall suggest a peaceful and chill interior. Around this cold giant, piping hot foods and beverages float in mid-air, encapsulated in transparent ice, as if frozen instantly in the presence of the fridge. The surroundings bring to mind a magical haven of frozen foods, devoid of any living creatures or textual elements.
